CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B7, reads: "PRINTING MANAGEMENT student Norman J. Toles, of Baton Rouge La., received his Bachelor of Science Degree at Tech."
